1031.question: what previous RNN models do they compare with?
1031.response: {'Answer': 'The paper compares the proposed PRU model with LSTM,  the skip-connection LSTM (Melis et al., 2018), the AWD-LSTM (Merity et al., 2018), the variational LSTM (Gal and Ghahramani, 2016), and the Quantized LSTM (Xu et al., 2018).'}
1031.answer: Variational LSTM, CharCNN, Pointer Sentinel-LSTM, RHN, NAS Cell, SRU, QRNN, RAN, 4-layer skip-connection LSTM, AWD-LSTM, Quantized LSTM
